WEBVTT

1
00:00:55.125 --> 00:00:56.333
I did it!

2
00:00:56.833 --> 00:00:58.290
Holy shit!

3
00:00:58.291 --> 00:00:59.790
It…

4
00:00:59.791 --> 00:01:01.249
Was…

5
00:01:01.250 --> 00:01:02.582
Awesome.

6
00:01:02.583 --> 00:01:03.665
Start from the top!

7
00:01:03.666 --> 00:01:06.083
I walked into school this morning.

8
00:01:08.125 --> 00:01:10.249
And then I see Colin Corwin.

9
00:01:10.250 --> 00:01:13.791
- Yeah!
<i>- Somebody said you got a new friend.</i>

10
00:01:18.583 --> 00:01:22.583
<i>Does she love you better than I can?</i>

11
00:01:25.416 --> 00:01:27.416
Jill tastes like beef jerky.

12
00:01:34.833 --> 00:01:38.249
I see you told everyone how you begged me to suck face.

13
00:01:38.250 --> 00:01:40.290
- Classy!
- Ooh!

14
00:01:40.291 --> 00:01:43.540
Sorry. Jill. but I'm <i>not</i> gonna be your boyfriend.

15
00:01:43.541 --> 00:01:46.499
- Oh!
- Don't flatter yourself. Colin Corwin.

16
00:01:46.500 --> 00:01:50.041
I regretted you the second
your sweaty slug lips touched mine.

17
00:01:51.125 --> 00:01:54.624
Hey. Jill. does your sister taste like beef jerky too.

18
00:01:54.625 --> 00:01:56.499
or just… cancer?

19
00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:57.957
Cold.

20
00:01:57.958 --> 00:02:00.625
<i>I'm just gonna dance all night…</i>

21
00:02:01.583 --> 00:02:03.499
Fight!

22
00:02:03.500 --> 00:02:07.750
Fight! Fight! Fight!

23
00:02:10.666 --> 00:02:13.249
You're gonna be in so much trouble.

24
00:02:13.250 --> 00:02:14.333
Mr. Corwin!

25
00:02:15.500 --> 00:02:17.666
You cry like a little bitch.

26
00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:21.915
He asked if I tasted like cancer?

27
00:02:21.916 --> 00:02:22.957
That's it?

28
00:02:22.958 --> 00:02:25.832
I'd rather have cancer than cystic fibrosis.

29
00:02:25.833 --> 00:02:28.707
Boys are just so embarrassing.

30
00:02:28.708 --> 00:02:30.832
Well. congratulations. You're suspended.

31
00:02:30.833 --> 00:02:31.833
Again.

32
00:02:34.833 --> 00:02:38.458
<i>Welcome to the culinary motherland. San Francisco.</i>

33
00:02:39.333 --> 00:02:43.041
<i>I just gotta see it for myself.</i>

34
00:02:43.541 --> 00:02:47.457
<i>I'm in the corner Watching you kiss her.</i>

35
00:02:47.458 --> 00:02:50.291
<i>Oh.</i>

36
00:02:51.333 --> 00:02:52.333
Turmeric.

37
00:02:53.333 --> 00:02:55.540
Pistachio. fruit of the gods!

38
00:02:55.541 --> 00:02:58.541
<i>Oh!</i>

39
00:02:59.958 --> 00:03:01.958
<i>I'm giving it my all...</i>

40
00:03:03.791 --> 00:03:05.833
Back away. girls! Out of the way!

41
00:03:12.750 --> 00:03:14.375
We shoulda had boys.

42
00:03:14.958 --> 00:03:19.707
You see. the antibiotics aren't working
as well as we'd hoped.

43
00:03:19.708 --> 00:03:20.665
Hi.

44
00:03:20.666 --> 00:03:22.916
Izzy. listen. It's Robyn.

45
00:03:25.541 --> 00:03:28.165
<i>On my own…</i>

46
00:03:28.166 --> 00:03:29.957
- Ready?
- Ready!

47
00:03:29.958 --> 00:03:32.000
<i>On my own.</i>

48
00:03:48.041 --> 00:03:52.707
<i>So far away. but still so near…</i>

49
00:03:52.708 --> 00:03:55.874
Do you really need to go out?
It's your last New Year's with us.

50
00:03:55.875 --> 00:03:57.249
I know.

51
00:03:57.250 --> 00:03:59.665
It's also my last New Year's with my friends.

52
00:03:59.666 --> 00:04:00.915
- I know.
- Bye. love you!

53
00:04:00.916 --> 00:04:01.832
- Be safe.
- Mwah! Bye!

54
00:04:01.833 --> 00:04:04.333
- Love you.
<i>- To say goodbye.</i>

55
00:04:04.958 --> 00:04:06.333
You ready?

56
00:04:06.833 --> 00:04:11.040
15 minutes to midnight. bitches!

57
00:04:11.041 --> 00:04:14.083
I'm sorry. I have gotta go. I can't…

58
00:04:23.041 --> 00:04:25.582
- I'm so sorry.
- No.

59
00:04:25.583 --> 00:04:27.291
That was so fun.

60
00:04:29.416 --> 00:04:31.999
- Sorry. Pardon me. Excuse me.
<i>- I'm giving it my all.</i>

61
00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:36.499
<i>But I'm not the girl You're taking home…</i>

62
00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:39.207
Three. two. one!

63
00:04:39.208 --> 00:04:42.166
Happy New Year!

64
00:04:50.708 --> 00:04:53.999
I have my knife skills test tomorrow.
and there's just no way for me

65
00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:57.082
to make it in time and I am so. so sorry.

66
00:04:57.083 --> 00:04:58.124
Holy sh…

67
00:04:58.125 --> 00:05:00.249
<i>Don't worry. my lad.</i>

68
00:05:00.250 --> 00:05:03.707
<i>Pretty soon. you'll be headed to the culinary motherland!</i>

69
00:05:03.708 --> 00:05:05.665
<i>Dancing on my own…</i>

70
00:05:05.666 --> 00:05:09.624
He thought it was gonna happen in 2029. 30 years ago.

71
00:05:09.625 --> 00:05:11.916
so if we can just…

72
00:05:13.208 --> 00:05:15.374
Oh. you're looking at my eye.

73
00:05:15.375 --> 00:05:18.458
- Your eye? What?
- Yeah. I look like Sloth from <i>The Goonies</i>.

74
00:05:19.541 --> 00:05:20.999
- No. you don't.
- I know.

75
00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:23.124
- No. you don't.
- Don't worry. It's…

76
00:05:23.125 --> 00:05:24.291
It's just pink eye.

77
00:05:25.625 --> 00:05:28.874
Well. I'm pretty sure pink eye is. like. super contagious.

78
00:05:28.875 --> 00:05:32.124
No. that's just a common misconception.

79
00:05:32.125 --> 00:05:33.915
No. really. I think it is.

80
00:05:33.916 --> 00:05:35.666
Fake news made up by Big Pharma.

81
00:05:37.250 --> 00:05:38.499
Trust me.

82
00:05:38.500 --> 00:05:41.208
Your eyes. on the other hand. are super beautiful.

83
00:05:44.250 --> 00:05:47.624
<i>Your call has been forwarded to voicemail.</i>

84
00:05:47.625 --> 00:05:51.332
And then he smears butt particles all over my face.

85
00:05:51.333 --> 00:05:54.749
My face is a butthole.

86
00:05:54.750 --> 00:05:58.166
Call me tomorrow. please.

87
00:06:09.041 --> 00:06:10.041
I'm up.

88
00:06:18.333 --> 00:06:23.916
<i>I'm just young enough To be a little numb and dumb.</i>

89
00:06:27.583 --> 00:06:33.208
<i>Not sure how I feel But I'm sure I've seen enough.</i>

90
00:06:36.750 --> 00:06:40.582
<i>Enough that the world Would miss me a little.</i>

91
00:06:40.583 --> 00:06:41.916
<i>Would they say I...</i>

92
00:06:49.041 --> 00:06:53.790
<i>Here we are. here we are.</i>

93
00:06:53.791 --> 00:06:58.457
<i>Hey.</i>

94
00:06:58.458 --> 00:07:00.749
<i>Here we are. here we are.</i>

95
00:07:00.750 --> 00:07:04.250
<i>It's like I'm almost happy.</i>

96
00:07:05.291 --> 00:07:09.125
<i>It's like I'm almost happy.</i>

97
00:07:45.458 --> 00:07:46.624
<i>Bonjour!</i>

98
00:07:46.625 --> 00:07:49.249
Chef Bastien. who is your favorite chef?

99
00:07:49.250 --> 00:07:51.915
Who is my favorite chef? That is easy.

100
00:07:51.916 --> 00:07:53.582
It is <i>ma mère.</i>

101
00:07:53.583 --> 00:07:56.165
She is so beautiful. she is dead.

102
00:07:56.166 --> 00:07:59.166
Your performance on <i>Top Chef</i> changed my life.

103
00:08:01.416 --> 00:08:02.416
Ow.

104
00:08:05.541 --> 00:08:08.208
Geoffrey! Eyes on your cake!

105
00:08:08.958 --> 00:08:10.666
Get!

106
00:08:11.625 --> 00:08:13.458
Look at me. Don't look at me.

107
00:08:14.791 --> 00:08:15.875
Look at me.

108
00:08:16.750 --> 00:08:18.291
Never look at me!

109
00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:26.999
Did you just look at me?
Did you just make eye contact with me?

110
00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:28.500
No. Chef.

111
00:08:36.791 --> 00:08:38.207
Oh!

112
00:08:38.208 --> 00:08:40.541
Maybe try saying "corner" next time.

113
00:08:51.083 --> 00:08:52.207
- You okay?
- Yeah.

114
00:08:52.208 --> 00:08:57.124
Eight hours deseeding and slicing kumquats?!

115
00:08:57.125 --> 00:08:58.290
Culinary water boarding.

116
00:08:58.291 --> 00:09:01.624
I can't even remember
the last time I actually made anything.

117
00:09:01.625 --> 00:09:03.832
other than my brekkie burrito.

118
00:09:03.833 --> 00:09:08.874
All I do is measure. deseed. slice.
and pray for the sweet release of death.

119
00:09:08.875 --> 00:09:11.790
An AI robot could do my job better than me.

120
00:09:11.791 --> 00:09:14.124
<i>You were built for this. my dude.</i>

121
00:09:14.125 --> 00:09:15.291
Let a mofo know.

122
00:09:16.750 --> 00:09:19.707
I will let a mofo know I am homesick.

123
00:09:19.708 --> 00:09:22.999
I'm almost out of savings. and there's nowhere for me to go

124
00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:25.915
unless a baker quits or retires or dies.

125
00:09:25.916 --> 00:09:27.915
All right. fine. you crazy son of a bitch.

126
00:09:27.916 --> 00:09:30.540
I will fly to San Fran
and murder one of the bakers with you.

127
00:09:30.541 --> 00:09:31.915
How would we do it?

128
00:09:31.916 --> 00:09:34.915
Well. obviously. we'd wrap my oxygen cord around his neck.

129
00:09:34.916 --> 00:09:38.499
Wow. you answered that so quickly.

130
00:09:38.500 --> 00:09:41.832
Wait. speaking of lack of oxygen to the brain.

131
00:09:41.833 --> 00:09:43.999
I'm getting drinks with Equinox Ethan tomorrow.

132
00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:47.124
Isn't that the guy who thinks
that babies can breathe underwater?

133
00:09:47.125 --> 00:09:48.165
He's neurospicy.

134
00:09:48.166 --> 00:09:50.540
Have a little healthy self-love. my guy.

135
00:09:50.541 --> 00:09:51.541
Eh…

136
00:09:52.333 --> 00:09:53.999
You've gotta get on Hinge.

137
00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:55.332
<i>It's amazing.</i>

138
00:09:55.333 --> 00:09:58.415
Except for the part where you feel
like a hideous. unlovable troll

139
00:09:58.416 --> 00:10:00.041
that might match with Ted Bundy.

140
00:10:00.708 --> 00:10:03.082
I've never been drier.

141
00:10:03.083 --> 00:10:06.165
I think I'd rather just live vicariously through you.

142
00:10:06.166 --> 00:10:07.166
<i>Perfect.</i>

143
00:10:10.958 --> 00:10:12.457
- Hello?
<i>- Yeah. I'm here.</i>

144
00:10:12.458 --> 00:10:13.957
- Hi.
<i>- No…</i>

145
00:10:13.958 --> 00:10:16.499
I have to tell you something. Don't freak out.

146
00:10:16.500 --> 00:10:17.500
