In an "order" of things.

209
00:14:36.500 --> 00:14:38.833
I think she would have really loved Burning Man.

210
00:14:41.916 --> 00:14:45.082
So. um… today.

211
00:14:45.083 --> 00:14:47.500
rather than eviscerating this…

212
00:14:49.625 --> 00:14:51.832
Order of things that I don't understand.

213
00:14:51.833 --> 00:14:54.040
um. I'm gonna try my best.

214
00:14:54.041 --> 00:14:57.458
I'm gonna try my best to make lemonade. like Izzy.

215
00:14:58.291 --> 00:14:59.583
And Beyoncé.

216
00:15:04.916 --> 00:15:07.832
Isabelle could have been alive a thousand years ago.

217
00:15:07.833 --> 00:15:09.290
or a thousand years from now.

218
00:15:09.291 --> 00:15:13.165
but what are the chances
that in all of time. space. humanity.

219
00:15:13.166 --> 00:15:16.208
she was alive with <i>us.</i> right?

220
00:15:18.791 --> 00:15:19.916
With me.

221
00:15:21.333 --> 00:15:24.666
How lucky are we? And not only did she and I meet.

222
00:15:28.625 --> 00:15:29.625
But…

223
00:15:33.375 --> 00:15:35.916
But we got to eat pancakes.

224
00:15:36.833 --> 00:15:40.290
We got to… wiggle out our little baby teeth together.

225
00:15:40.291 --> 00:15:42.625
We got to paint each other's toenails.

226
00:15:47.791 --> 00:15:49.500
We got to be sisters.

227
00:15:51.916 --> 00:15:53.750
We got to be sisters.

228
00:15:54.416 --> 00:15:59.750
<i>Built a home.</i>

229
00:16:01.083 --> 00:16:02.666
<i>For you.</i>

230
00:16:04.375 --> 00:16:07.250
<i>For me.</i>

231
00:16:08.166 --> 00:16:15.125
<i>Until it disappeared.</i>

232
00:16:17.000 --> 00:16:19.125
<i>From me.</i>

233
00:16:20.291 --> 00:16:23.500
<i>From you.</i>

234
00:16:27.958 --> 00:16:32.041
<i>My brother in Christ. We miss you on Whore Island.</i>

235
00:16:35.916 --> 00:16:39.165
<i>My brother in Christ. We miss you on Whore Island.</i>

236
00:16:39.166 --> 00:16:42.457
<i>Don't forget. You're more beautiful than Cinderella.</i>

237
00:16:42.458 --> 00:16:46.957
<i>You smell like pine needles.
and you have a face like sunshine.</i>

238
00:16:46.958 --> 00:16:50.665
<i>When I look at you. my heart is filled
with purple and pink fireworks.</i>

239
00:16:50.666 --> 00:16:51.665
<i>Be ungovernable.</i>

240
00:16:51.666 --> 00:16:53.374
<i>You gotta flop to fly.</i>

241
00:16:53.375 --> 00:16:57.165
<i>We could open a chowder spot
and call it "Bisquey Business."</i>

242
00:16:57.166 --> 00:17:00.707
<i>I just drank all of Mom's rosé and DMed Jacob Elordi.</i>

243
00:17:00.708 --> 00:17:03.458
<i>Maybe he'll think I'm a Make-a-Wish kid.</i>

244
00:17:04.125 --> 00:17:06.333
<i>Good night. lad. I love you.</i>

245
00:17:07.375 --> 00:17:08.416
<i>Call me.</i>

246
00:17:55.000 --> 00:17:56.000
Who is that?

247
00:17:56.666 --> 00:17:59.250
I don't know. I just got a new work cell.

248
00:18:01.333 --> 00:18:05.540
Yo. Isabella!

249
00:18:05.541 --> 00:18:07.499
It is I. your brother.

250
00:18:07.500 --> 00:18:10.665
